.DS_Store
# Live yalc snapshot of the workspace's lib build (per-pair yalc store). The
# `file:.yalc/...` dep in package.json is a stable path that gets repopulated
# by `yalc add` on setup and refreshed in-place by the lib's `yalc:watch` on
# every dist rebuild — same mechanism the hub uses for `openframe-frontend-core`.
.yalc
